      "comment": "AMAZIGH TORQUE (2) nice filly who brings a solid set of figures here third-up. Can go on with it today after she chased hard with a sound second over 1180m at Grafton. Should prove too strong for these from the low draw. WEEKEND ARTIST (8) is back after a break of five months. Has a decent first-up record and since fitted with a 1000m trial at the Gold Coast. Can make his presence felt. WITNESS DIS (9) resumes after failing to see the 1720m out when eighth at Grafton on November 30. Ran some okay races over the shorter trips and fitted with the one trial. TALES OF FORTUNE (1) Star Turn gelding from a Your Song mare on debut for the James Hepworth stable. Ran fourth in his latest trial over 900m at Beaudesert. Worth thought.",
